## Usage:
- PNG files can be viewed directly or embedded in documents
- Mermaid files can be rendered using:
  - Mermaid Live Editor (mermaid.live)
  - GitHub/GitLab markdown rendering
  - VS Code Mermaid extensions
  - Mermaid CLI tools
